abstract: "pmean is a Stata command for computing panel means and performing within-between decomposition for applied panel data analysis. It supports both two-dimensional and three-dimensional panel data. Adds third-dimension means and three-way decomposition, and includes optional full pairwise decomposition for three-dimensional panels. Version 2.0.1 sharpens variable labels for clarity, adds an optional listwise sample option, detects nested third-dimension variables and prints an informational note. The release is fully backward compatible with version 2.0.0."
